transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yes, uh, I ordered the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And never did get it. I got some kind of junk that ain't no good.

Speaker 1: Well, so did you receive something, or you didn't receive something?

Speaker 2: Yeah, I did. I received something.

Speaker 1: Like two days ago.

Speaker 2: So that's most likely the Viagra AGV, sir. Um, what does the marking on the pill say on there?

Speaker 1: It's got a tab zero on it.

Speaker 2: Got it. So that's going to be the Viagra AGV, sir. The AGV has the milligram dose engraved on the pill.

Speaker 1: The standard ones, the basic ones, have AC and a number on there, but the one that you got is the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 2: Well, it ain't no good.

Speaker 1: You give it a try? It also has a 90-day guarantee. Call us back if you have any other questions.

Speaker 2: It also has a what?

Speaker 1: A 90-day guarantee.

Speaker 2: Okay, and what if it don't work? Then what?

Speaker 1: That's exactly why it has a 90-day guarantee, sir. So if it doesn't work out for you, send the remaining pills back for a reason.

Speaker 2: Yeah, okay. All right. See you.

Speaker 1: No problem. Yeah, have a good one.
